title: SIW Viewer 1.0
description:
Copied from SIW Homepage:


SIW Viewer is used to show XML Reports created by SIW.

Microsoft .NET Framework Version 2.0 is required.


"This is a free version for PERSONAL usage, NOT for commercial usage!"


Comments from the uploader (olofolleola4):
This XML-viewer can only open XML reports that are exported from the Business or the Technician's version.
So you can't export XML reports from the freeware versions of SIW.
